{"tid":802461,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測) 轟天猛將1-3","createTime":"2018-09-01T13:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T16:53:00.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c995fbad5e6e688ff923f1fbd28b43fc1455991","tid":802461,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ca6ca36a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5c53eef3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3168f56e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/images/stories/114/2012/09/20120918filmExpendables2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F114%2F2012%2F09%2F20120918filmExpendables2.jpg&h=64523bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f3/轟天猛將.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff3%2F%E8%BD%9F%E5%A4%A9%E7%8C%9B%E5%B0%87.jpg&h=7b0fef84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yz4OSgZmMChsWlGe04mdBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/4338ea1fdd8260dbf86681277e178f0f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fyz4OSgZmMChsWlGe04mdBw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F4338ea1fdd8260dbf86681277e178f0f&h=07f13d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.巴尼支付了原協議要求的三百萬美元以保障人質安全，但海盜卻坐地起價要求五百萬。岡納則打算直接交火，引致海盜傷亡。岡納隨後因為對被俘的海盜動用私刑，而引發與「陰陽」之間的鬥毆，最後為巴尼所制止，由於岡納太過暴躁，精神極不穩定，巴尼將之驅逐出隊...<br />\n<br />\n2.這支傭兵組成的突擊隊由巴尼（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）領軍，經過激烈的槍戰，解救了中國富豪和戰壕（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾），最終陰陽（李連杰飾）負責把商人護送回中國，陰陽就此下場。<br />\n回美國後，隊員比利（連恩&middot;漢斯沃飾）說他打算退出，到法國和女朋友團聚。巴尼答應了他的要求。<br />\n接著，巴尼接到了一個中情局情報員「教堂先生」（布魯斯&middot;威利飾）的新任務：去一架墜落在阿爾巴尼亞的中國空軍運輸機上，取回保險箱裏的秘密物品。同時在「教堂先生」的推薦下，華裔女性的陳美琪（余男飾）加入隊伍..<br />\n<br />\n3.浴血幫領導人巴尼&middot;羅斯（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）帶領著手下李&middot;聖誕（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）、岡納&middot;詹森（杜夫&middot;朗格林飾）和托爾&middot;羅德（蘭迪&middot;寇楚飾）襲擊一輛前往軍事監獄的列車，幫助巴尼的老友死亡醫生（衛斯里&middot;史奈普飾）出來。死亡醫生被救出後，獨自一人解決列車上的士兵，並讓列車失控直衝監獄、造成監獄大爆炸。死亡醫生接受了巴尼的招募，回到了浴血幫。之後一行人到索馬利亞執行一件軍火商的彈藥走私任務，在那與海爾&middot;凱撒（泰瑞&middot;克魯斯飾）會合後展開行動。當中巴尼驚訝地發現，負責走私的軍火商就是浴血幫初期的聯合創始人康拉德&middot;史東班克斯（梅爾&middot;吉勃遜飾），原本走上歪路的他應早被巴尼解決，沒想到還活著。康拉德發現巴尼等人後隨即上了直升機，拿狙擊槍重傷凱撒並投下炸彈攻擊他們，之後便離去...<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *有時間先播埋3<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2fbdee66\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=998494db\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdd556045f52d5f61b485b443c85102649eb6c6","tid":802461,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ce85bead81a47e5078817be0794fd8c4836872","tid":802461,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5dd238b5a4bc4423d31a7a3ceeb81098f65bb0","tid":802461,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e98abc022e632dfb912b8c79eaf8b3706f563a1","tid":802461,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f738e22c227ed1b55dad038aeb286089a720de","tid":802461,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}